      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's insane. if there were actually hieroglyphics and geometric structures, it would change everything we know about human history. why would they go to such extreme lengths to hide it? it feels like they aren't just protecting us from panic, it feels like they're protecting the existence of this discovery itself. do you think there's any way to find out if any of this tech or info was moved to a private facility after the missions?",
